Both Swiss banks, UBS and Credit Suisse have supplanted this idea of the Swiss bank, but at some point - or betrayed how the head of a small Swiss private bank finds it.
He prefers not to read his name in the newspaper, after all, like all Swiss bankers, he also does business with the two big banks.
