Casino forgives Jonás Larrazábal, who comes free
After 72 days of silence, the agent of Casino Red released the brother of the mayor of Monterrey from the trial against him for alleged blackmail.
After 72 days of imprisonment, Manuel Jonás Larrazábal is released after the agent of Casino Red has awarded him a trial against the brother of the mayor of Monterrey for extortion before the Second Criminal Court of the District.
